CAF
Got Square Developer account
Started Square sandbox App

While working through the Sandbox app, I noticed that we can use Webhooks to get notified when a flight is booked

I got the Sandbox API to work using the Square test platform\.

I’m now trying to get postman to work\. Got it\. I can get postman to call the Square Sandbox and get test responses\.
